                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>Enter the rule name (i.e.: "Communication channel check"). This is the name of the rule that will be written in the fax, text message, e-mail and remote supervisor text.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>Select the time band when the activity is enabled</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="3">
